AWS Lambda:
Lambda lets you bulid and run code quickly, without provisionary or managing servers.
In amazon connect, you can invoke funcitons in a contact flow.
You can build lambda functions that communicate with your internal systems, such as retrieving the status of an order.
Can return the value from the functions.

Amazon Lens:
Amazon connect integrate with amazon lens to provide chat and voice. Amazon lens provide the automatic speech to text,
and NLU recognize customer intent.

Amazon S3:
stores data from amazon connect, such as recordings of conversations and metrics reports.

